data.description: Dont Miss this Spacious Brick Front, 3 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath Home featuring Hardwood Floors in Foyer, Separate Living Room and Separate Dining Room.   Vaulted Ceiling, Fireplace, Eat in Kitchen, Huge Finished Room in Basement that would be perfect for a Play Room, Office, Den or Man Cave.  Master Bedroom has a spacious Walk in Closet, Trey Ceiling, Separate Walk In Shower and Garden Tub.  2 Car Garage and Privacy Fenced in Back Yard. New HVAC just installed. 08/10/15
